{"lastUpdated":"2026-06-16T23:53:34.324Z","seriesId":95356,"title":"LEMON ANGEL PROJECT","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/31892005/31892005.37716290","descriptionFirst":"Lemon Angelが、突然の解散を発表してから数ヶ月後の春。白鴎学園高校に入学した智は、良き理解者であり憧れの存在だった唯の親友、元Lemon Angelのリーダー・美希に出会う。しかし、唯から聞いていたイメージとは掛け離れた美希の冷たい態度に智は困惑する。その帰り、智を尾行する謎の影が…。\n\n皆口 智:しほの涼／結城早夜:小清水亜美／渚砂みる:門脇 舞／エリカ・キャンベル:茅原実里／榊原冬美:平間樹里／諏訪美希:丸山美紀／鴻野 唯:清水香里／氷室慎也:子安武人\n\n原作:AMGエンタテインメント／シリーズ構成・脚本:たきもとまさし／キャラクターデザイン:渡邊由香里／監督:千葉大輔／チーフアニメーター:山川宏治／コンセプトデザイン:星の絵富也／美術監督:宮前光春／美術:獏プロダクション／色彩設定:佐々木雅人／音響制作:マルチックアイ／製作:れもんふぁーむ\n\n次話→so31892006","tags":["アイドル","RADIX","2006年冬アニメ","レモンエンジェル","ドラマ/青春"],"cours":"2006-冬","colKey":"ら","relatedSeries":[],"episodes":[{"contentId":"so31892005","episodeNo":1,"title":"LEMON ANGEL PROJECT　第1話　夢から覚めた天使","viewCounter":1500,"commentCounter":26,"mylistCounter":22,"lengthSeconds":1441,"startTime":"2012-06-27T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/31892005/31892005.37716290"},{"contentId":"so31892006","episodeNo":2,"title":"LEMON ANGEL PROJECT　第2話　Evolution","viewCounter":160,"commentCounter":19,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1441,"startTime":"2012-06-27T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/31892006/31892006.84554944"},{"contentId":"so31892007","episodeNo":3,"title":"LEMON ANGEL PROJECT　第3話　I will","viewCounter":159,"commentCounter":30,"mylistCounter":2,"lengthSeconds":1440,"startTime":"2012-06-27T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/31892007/31892007.96604452"},{"contentId":"so31892008","episodeNo":4,"title":"LEMON ANGEL PROJECT　第4話　Smile means love","viewCounter":115,"commentCounter":28,"mylistCounter":0,"lengthSeconds":1441,"startTime":"2012-06-27T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/31892008/31892008.11296275"},{"contentId":"so31892010","episodeNo":5,"title":"LEMON ANGEL PROJECT　第5話　友達でいいから","viewCounter":113,"commentCounter":21,"mylistCou